---
import AppShell from "../layouts/AppShell.astro";

const title = "Contacto";
---

<AppShell title={title}>
  <section class="space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-2">
      <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase">Contact</p>
      <h1 class="m-0 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">{title}</h1>
      <p class="m-0 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        Si tienes ideas, detectas un bug raro o quieres comentar un caso de uso, aquí tienes formas directas de escribirme.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/drespns/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer noopener"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/50 p-5 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900/40 transition-colors"
      >
        <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">LinkedIn</p>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">linkedin.com/in/drespns</p>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/drespns/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer noopener"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/50 p-5 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900/40 transition-colors"
      >
        <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">GitHub</p>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">github.com/drespns</p>
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:drespns@gmail.com"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-950/50 p-5 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900/40 transition-colors md:col-span-2"
      >
        <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Email</p>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">drespns@gmail.com</p>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 shadow-sm p-5 space-y-2">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-base font-semibold">Qué me sirve si reportas un problema</h2>
      <ul class="m-0 pl-5 list-disc space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>URL exacta y qué estabas haciendo</li>
        <li>Captura o vídeo corto si se entiende mejor</li>
        <li>Consola del navegador (si hay errores)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </section>
</AppShell>

